Wait for it! Michelle Malkin predicts #NextMaddowBombshell about Trump Posted at 11:34 am on March 15, 2017 by Doug P. 
With MSNBC’s great big Trump tax bombshell backfire now behind them, it’s time for Rachel Maddow to dig up the next scoop. Michelle Malkin knows where it’s all headed: #NextMaddowBombshell Two pages of Trump's algebra homework from 1960.
